<div class="header">
Ocean View Resort System Help
</div>

<div class="container">

<h2>How to Use the System</h2>

<ul>

<li><b>Add Reservation</b> – Use this option to add a new guest reservation to the system.</li>

<li><b>Search Reservation</b> – Allows you to search reservation details using the Reservation ID.</li>

<li><b>Delete Reservation</b> – Remove an existing reservation record from the system.</li>

<li><b>Generate Bill</b> – Calculate the total bill based on room type and number of nights.</li>

<li><b>Logout</b> – Securely logout from the system.</li>

</ul>

